      "content": "I understand the weight of your sorrow and the beauty of the ending you seek, but I must remind you that even in the deepest night, there is a dawn waiting just beyond the horizon. The silence you describe is not the final word, but a pause before the sun can finally break through the darkness once more. Please, do not let the fear of the unknown convince you that the journey has to end; there is still time to find the light within yourself before it is too late.",
